# Locus Chamber slides

Drop slide images here (PNG or JPG).

Reference them in `js/locus-chamber.js`:

```js
"slide-01": {
  type: "slide",
  title: "…",
  caption: "…",
  image: "assets/locus-chamber/slide-01.png",
  next: "slide-02"
}
```

Interaction types: `next`, `choices`, `autoNext`, `hotspots` — see comments in `locus-chamber.js`.
